{"tid":1815270,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"〔國際戰線〕澳洲好需要國際支援","createTime":"2020-01-07T11:37:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T06:09:30.000Z","uid":165752,"like":81,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"01cc501c41de3056a69ce6376c312d193e2c99df","tid":1815270,"uid":165752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T11:37:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>如果你認為香港嘅手足都未顧掂就去幫外國，</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁諗真係太短視！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n過去咁多個月，成日向外界話出咗咩事，有咩人道危機，要支援香港。好啦，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">而家外國有事，係時侯到香港幫外國，係時侯話全世界聽香港人願意 stand with Australia。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n澳洲有冇幫過香港，邊個幫先幫後根本唔係重點，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>幫人係講 timing，邊個幾時有需要嘅咪去幫。</strong></span>唔通你會要求美國先立人權法，至批准美國利用香港作為美中談判嘅籌碼？<br />\n<br />\n既然澳洲都開到聲要 support，點解唔做個順水人情，幫佢一把。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">到最後籌款額夠多 make 到 noise，自然會令更多澳洲人關心香港，</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">甚至令原先唔支持香港嘅澳洲人對向香港人改觀。</span></strong>坦白講，澳洲人未必清楚香港發生緊咩事，你會唔會無拏拏走去關心外國發生咩事？<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">好多時人嘅立場係對人唔對事</span></strong>，like 你嘅更過份嘅事會撐，唔like 你嘅唞啖氣都會嘈，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">只要令澳洲人對香港人産生好感，就成功咗第一步。</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">到時多咗民意撐香港，國會方面自然易辦事</span></strong>，需知道佢哋最終都係向選民交代。<br />\n<br />\n如果香港援助澳洲能夠喺國際上得到關注，可以畀各國知香港願意參與國際事務，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">用行動說明香港人同西方同一陣線，令各國重新評估香港嘅價值，調整對華政策</span></strong>，有非常長遠嘅效果。<br />\n<br />\n送嘢畀人，最重要係切合用家需要，好多組織經已講明接受捐款。要做到上述效果，當然唔係每個人直接捐啦，人哋識你老鼠咩。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">就捐，要以「香港人」名義去捐</span></strong>，言下之意就係集資一炮過捐。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">而家「澳港聯」就搞咗個眾籌</span></span></strong><br />\n大家可以入去，唔需要理會上限，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">因為越多錢回音越大</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/support-australia-rural-firefighters?fbclid=IwAR3y0C3D0Y6Q5dvtigFIVkf-O2Z_5Tk15eH3KF8-rq0ySgKL0VJ-YyWQXyk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Fsupport-australia-rural-firefighters%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3y0C3D0Y6Q5dvtigFIVkf-O2Z_5Tk15eH3KF8-rq0ySgKL0VJ-YyWQXyk&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TfjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=8ca700c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gofundme.com/f/support-australia-rural-firefighters?fbclid=IwAR3y0C3D0Y6Q5dvtigFIVkf-O2Z_5Tk15eH3KF8-rq0ySgKL0VJ-YyWQXyk</a><br />\n澳港聯原post在此<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=2467098240221292&amp;id=1764116977186092\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2467098240221292%26id%3D1764116977186092&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TfjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=41a91152\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=2467098240221292&amp;id=1764116977186092</a><br />\n<br />\n我想強調我同澳港聯毫無關係，有問題請直接聯絡澳港聯<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"579d0557451711fa7b8f43b4d832b0ab7b14d9b1","tid":1815270,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T11:37:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"02b5c88dec0c9dabd44d29e3225c39e6ef6865cd","tid":1815270,"uid":165752,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T11:38:12.000Z","msg":"澳洲山火持續咗幾個月，超過五億隻可愛嘅小動物俾無情嘅大火吞噬，僥幸逃出生天嘅就無家可歸，佢哋好需要你嘅幫忙。<br />\n<br />\n一班喺澳洲嘅香港人好有心整咗個眾籌，快啲捐錢畀澳洲，等佢哋快啲撲熄場火。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/support-australia-rural-firefighters?fbclid=IwAR3y0C3D0Y6Q5dvtigFIVkf-O2Z_5Tk15eH3KF8-rq0ySgKL0VJ-YyWQXyk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Fsupport-australia-rural-firefighters%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3y0C3D0Y6Q5dvtigFIVkf-O2Z_5Tk15eH3KF8-rq0ySgKL0VJ-YyWQXyk&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TfjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=8ca700c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gofundme.com/f/support-australia-rural-firefighters?fbclid=IwAR3y0C3D0Y6Q5dvtigFIVkf-O2Z_5Tk15eH3KF8-rq0ySgKL0VJ-YyWQXyk</a><br />\n<br />\n<