slike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63f6448125f42446160e5a8f56b771acf67f0fde","tid":1815270,"uid":251660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T16:44:44.000Z","msg":"澳港聯咩底"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T17:04:33.000Z","msg":"反送中、支持普世價值嘅居澳港人，可以睇下佢哋 fb page page 再作決定"},{"pid":"b04ad7923ddf5fed60e04edd7020acc1b9e5421c","tid":1815270,"uid":184433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T17:04:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aba65e9f9a97a5ea7a714aa1baaaa38d6d8e6cab","tid":1815270,"uid":34594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T17:06:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6fe3d220452caed700216c8d602846432874511a","tid":1815270,"uid":183536,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T19:36:01.000Z","msg":"#國際戰線<br />\n#黃<br />\n#形象工程<br />\n#和理非必做<br />\n<br />\n香港人唔可以只係顧自己， 我哋要將黃藍經濟圈推出國際🌏!<br />\n<br />\n#黃金經濟圈 #香港抗爭者 #撐澳洲 之 #贊助樹熊挑戰 <br />\n<br />\n近期澳洲🇦🇺有大規模山火🔥，只要捐款小小錢救1隻🐨(AUD40=HKD213)，就可以幫香港抗爭者加少少光環🌟!<br />\n<br />\n唔使等前線，和理非快黎救🐨! 做好啲個形像，第日移民🐌或者去旅行💼，好多🦘都會感激我哋㗎!<br />\n<br />\n1. 上樹熊醫院🏥網頁<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.koalahospital.org.au/adopt-a-koala\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.koalahospital.org.au%2Fadopt-a-koala&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TfjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=efcf2c71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.koalahospital.org.au/adopt-a-koala</a><br />\n2. 揀隻可愛樹熊🐨<br />\n3. 揀✔ EAdoption<br />\n4. 地區係香港，地址隨意📝<br />\n3. 填你個名(可考慮:爭取普選)➡️Hong Kong Universal Suffragists<br />\n4. 去check out購物車🛒<br />\n5. 填信用卡💳號碼等資料<br />\n6. 完成<br />\n7. 🐨certificate 寄到你電郵📧<br />\n8. 可以reply及貼到我的tweeter，已tag了澳洲傳媒及政客!推到上報📰!<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LoveProtestinHK/status/1214604066602377216?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLoveProtestinHK%2Fstatus%2F1214604066602377216%3Fs%3D09&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TfjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=74be6b20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLoveProtestinHK%2Fstatus%2F1214604066602377216%3Fs%3D09&h=5eacc668\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/LoveProtestinHK/status/1214604066602377216?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n大家快點行動，🐨🐨好需要我們。澳洲都推動緊Magnitsky Act，通過左先可以制裁⚔⚔到中共走狗🐕教育局長楊潤雄🐊!"},{"pid":"8dcbf58db8dcd2d83ec833dc6ee1c804c2c14f9c","tid":1815270,"uid":237222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T19:39:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf2a6335b41a186960915118d3d99b304aeb1a78","tid":1815270,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63f6448125f42446160e5a8f56b771acf67f0fde","tid":1815270,"uid":251660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T16:44:44.000Z","msg":"澳港聯咩底"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T19:39:44.000Z","msg":"港人澳洲戰線page"},{"pid":"3a95a061d678468941d0d6ba815ce96def2bc1d6","tid":1815270,"uid":251660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T19:48:21.000Z","msg":"可以搞個聲援國際/全球抗共嘅集會<br />\n順便搞籌錢"},{"pid":"607ac6b75e73d1a647f4ee493cdb8a34c0ce9b25","tid":1815270,"uid":201031,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fd01809cb0a4b029c61a88084509598ff32a1c29","tid":1815270,"uid":165752,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8a291707da3b2a79899dd732cf3db83ebdca023b","tid":1815270,"uid":83692,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T15:03:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你班崇洋撚</span><br />\n<br />\n非洲冇飯食唔見你幫<br />\n中東比美國打唔見你幫<br />\n自己國家有難唔見你幫<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color